{"tid":408901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［宅男美夢］北大推「共享校花」，每人5分鐘。宣傳：我下面給你吃","createTime":"2017-09-21T15:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T15:30:49.000Z","uid":41351,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1561ba96a23c8651a7597e35572327e94e3d022d","tid":408901,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"內地共享經濟大行其道，但同時衍生不少借「共享」為噱頭的低俗營銷活動。繼早有有情趣用品商推出「共享女友」服務，有手機應用程式（App）營運商為推廣宣傳，竟在北京某大學的學生宿舍外舉行「共享校花」活動，聲稱掃QR Code（二維碼）就可以「與校花談5分鐘戀愛」，引起爭議。 <br />\n<br />\n從網傳照片可見，在北京交通大學校外學生公寓區，15名身穿統一白襯衣、格子短裙的「校花」列隊站在「共享校花停放點」上。而「校花」身後的布景板上寫道：「Hello單身狗，領個校花做你的五分鐘女友。」四周又放着寫有「別說話，吻我」、「我下面（麵）給你吃」等標語的紙牌。 <br />\n<br />\n事發後網上議論紛紛，有不少網民直指活動低俗、惡心、意淫。又有網民認為在學校發起這種活動，實在有傷風化。惟也有網民不以為意，並留意到有小狗也去了排隊，笑稱那應該是隻「單身狗」。 <br />\n<br />\n北京交通大學事後發表聲明，稱有傳媒公司未經校方批准，在校園外的學生公寓區舉行「校花活動」，學校發現後已即時叫停活動並清場。校方對此表示強烈憤慨，將進一步調查並向相關人員追究法律責任。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/230721_035403e696ad05688e57e2582fcef5c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F230721_035403e696ad05688e57e2582fcef5c5.jpg&h=756af388&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/230722_444608a05f1bd425107d7e1807dace96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F230722_444608a05f1bd425107d7e1807dace96.jpg&h=b6663317&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/230723_dc3326721014f1e49385f91f65a945d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F230723_dc3326721014f1e49385f91f65a945d4.jpg&h=308f2785&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/230723_dfce76059d906f065620fa5cd1d26905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F230723_dfce76059d906f065620fa5cd1d26905.jpg&h=02a456f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e37dbc056d5a9cae4dc356f1646e29fab6c5ed85","tid":408901,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"6c183d3992c3e8b494776559f7c9ffe694717823","tid":408901,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e7088108137765d716e227b60ce7dca7770185","tid":408901,"uid":31254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"共享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =公廁"},{"pid":"ad7fff9dfa7c6aae916bc76b4fa808df15ae4da0","tid":408901,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:14:07.000Z","msg":"5分鐘，夠爆一個血氣方剛男生"},{"pid":"b7e31192f417771f5c451ed43f6e7d3550930f8a","tid":408901,"uid":99051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:16:47.000Z","msg":"冇寫幾錢既 分分鐘貴過Ptgf"},{"pid":"ec8c37fa6c480ddf586d4b8acf88281d14973e3c","tid":408901,"uid":5462,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母有隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fac5b5af0f9b34080e097e472486b2600